Hello,<br>
<br>
No. Each hwloc-bind command in the mpirun above doesn't know that there
are other hwloc-bind instances on the same machine. All of them bind
their process to all cores in the first socket.</div><div id="yiv1189411888"><br></div><div id="yiv1189411888"><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">=&gt; Agree. For&nbsp;</span><span>socket:0.core:0-3</span><span style="font-size: 10pt; ">&nbsp;,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: black; ">hwloc will bind the MPI processes to all cores in the first socket. But how are the individual processes mapped on these cores? Will it be in this order:</span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; "><br></span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">rank 0&nbsp;</span><span
 style="font-family: Wingdings; color: black; "><span>à</span></span><span style="color: black; ">&nbsp;core 0</span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">rank 1&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Wingdings; color: black; "><span>à</span></span><span style="color: black; ">&nbsp;core 1</span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">rank 2&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Wingdings; color: black; "><span>à</span></span><span style="color: black; ">&nbsp;core 2</span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">rank 3&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Wingdings;
 color: black; "><span>à</span></span><span style="color: black; ">&nbsp;core 3</span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; "><br></span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">Or in this *arbitrary* order:</span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; "><br></span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">rank 0&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Wingdings; color: black; "><span>à</span></span><span style="color: black; ">&nbsp;core
 1</span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">rank 1&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Wingdings; color: black; "><span>à</span></span><span style="color: black; ">&nbsp;core 3</span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">rank 2&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Wingdings; color: black; "><span>à</span></span><span style="color: black; ">&nbsp;core 0</span></p><p class="yiv234151128MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 14.4pt; "><span style="color: black; ">rank 3&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Wingdings; color: black; "><span>à</span></span><span style="color: black; ">&nbsp;core 2</span></p>
